attributionInfo.brokerName: MOSSY OAK PROPERTIES INDIANA LAND AND LIFESTYLE

data.description: Rare New Goshen property! Enjoy nature in this country home located on just over an acre of land! This home has 2 upstairs bedrooms with a main level bathroom/laundry combo. The main living area features a large window overlooking the front yard. The dining room could also be used for an additional family room space. Upstairs you will find a large landing area that could be used as a bonus or rec. space. The master bedroom includes two large closets and the second bedroom is currently being used as storage. The 2-car detached garage has plenty of workshop space. Call today!
